data.description: - Seller is offering UP TO $5,000 towards buyer's closing costs!    This spacious 5 bed 3.5 bath HISTORIC home is situated on a large corner lot in the heart of Charleston within walking distance from parks and the Hiwassee River, including a public boat ramp. Location is between Chattanooga & Knoxville and provides easy access to I-75 with a short drive to Cleveland & Athens. The size of the home and the extra large storage building provides endless opportunities, including an extra bath in the attic that's ready for connections. Come enjoy the original character of this historic home and all the area has to offer! Information is deemed reliable but not guaranteed. Buyer/buyer's agent to verify all information.
